the scope of this course on
municipal solid waste management,

9
00:00:32,050 --> 00:00:35,570
but let me just give you a few words
on hazardous waste management.

10
00:00:36,540 --> 00:00:41,680
The main bulk of hazardous waste
is generated from chemical,

11
00:00:42,300 --> 00:00:47,040
industry, fertilizer and pesticide
manufacturing, petroleum

12
00:00:47,040 --> 00:00:50,850
and mining industry, and
also heavy steel industry.

13
